    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h3>Location Description</h3>
      <p>Every year, thousands of skiers and boarders journey to the Westcoast for an unrivalled ski vacation in Whistler Blackcomb. Theyâ€™re drawn by over 8100 skiable acres, a bustling pedestrian base village packed with shopping and dining choices, and a fantastic array of winter adventures.
